    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚通胀放缓幅度超过预期，为 2021 年以来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/colombian-inflation-slows-more-than-forecast-to-least-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚通胀率放缓幅度超过预期，降至 2021 年以来的最低水平，这支持了总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗 (Gustavo Petro) 加快货币宽松的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/colombian-inflation-slows-more-than-forecast-to-least-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高塔姆·阿达尼的侄子普拉纳夫谈论达拉维孟买贫民窟的重建</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/adani-s-nephew-spearheads-mumbai-slum-redevelopment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲最大贫民窟的重建项目由印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼的侄子普拉纳夫·阿达尼负责。达拉维贫民窟改造项目因电影《贫民窟的百万富翁》而闻名，该项目备受争议，引发了抗议和政治反对，但阿达尼家族认为这是孟买发展成为现代化城市的关键。普拉纳夫·阿达尼与彭博社的安东尼谈论了该项目给阿达尼集团带来的挑战。请观看彭博社特别电视连续剧《阿达尼内部》的最新一集。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/adani-s-nephew-spearheads-mumbai-slum-redevelopment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港保险业繁荣吸引内地求职者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hong-kong-s-insurance-boom-lures-job-seeking-mainlanders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大批来自内地金融和科技行业的专业人士涌入香港，他们对香港的职业和薪资前景感到失望。许多人试图通过兜售保险产品谋生并留在香港，这给曾经沉寂的保险业带来了一丝活力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hong-kong-s-insurance-boom-lures-job-seeking-mainlanders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市崩盘使新兴亚洲市场的焦点转向中国和马来西亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/stock-meltdown-turns-spotlight-on-em-asia-s-underowned-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周全球股市的动荡促使亚洲股市投资者将注意力转向近年来其持股量不断下降的市场，其中中国和马来西亚就是其中之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/stock-meltdown-turns-spotlight-on-em-asia-s-underowned-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国政策攻势彰显支持清洁能源的新决心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-s-policy-blitz-shows-fresh-resolve-to-support-clean-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们对能源安全的担忧逐渐消退，政府加大对陷入困境的绿色产业的支持，一系列政策声明凸显出中国对加快气候行动的信心日益增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-s-policy-blitz-shows-fresh-resolve-to-support-clean-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
